snippet.title: UEFA Striker - DreamON Preview Trailer
snippet.description:
Video taken from Dream ON Vol.1
Developer: Rage
Publisher: Infogrammes

Football action game featuring fast and exciting gameplay. Over 150 club and national aquads. Unique certification test mode. Extensive game editor and eight different competition modes.
